s')">✨ Moment</button></div></section><section class="prose-block guide-overview"><h2>Overview</h2><p>Bakes Thảo Điền 係草田區很順路的法式甜點 stop。相比普通 cafe，Bakes 嘅重點係精緻甜點同 croissant 類 pastry，適合 Day 3 逛完 Thảo Điền 小店後，用一小時坐低補糖、吹冷氣、整理戰利品。</p></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Highlights</h2><ul><li>多款法式甜點與千層 croissant</li><li>冷氣座位，適合午后避暑</li><li>同 The Dreamers Bakery 很近，可二選一</li></ul></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Good to Know</h2><ul><li>唔需要當成正式下午茶，4 人點 2–3 件 share 最剛好。</li><li>若當日太飽，可以外帶 pastry 留返酒店。</li></ul></section></main><div class="mini-menu" id="guideMenu"><button onclick="openGuideCategory('ATTRACTIONS')"><span><span class="menu-title">📍 ATTRACTIONS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('CAFÉS')"><span><span class="menu-title">☕ CAFÉS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('EXPERIENCE')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍳 EXPERIENCE</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('RESTAURANTS')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍽 RESTAURANTS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SHOP')"><span><span class="menu-title">🛍 SHOP</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SPA')"><span><span class="menu-title">💆 SPA</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('STAY')"><span><span class="menu-title">🏨 STAY</span></span><span>›</span></button></div><div class="mini-menu" id="tripMenu">
