ep-me-in')">✨ Moment</button></div></section><section class="prose-block guide-overview"><h2>Overview</h2><p>Bếp Mẹ Ỉn 是 Michelin Bib Gourmand 越式家常菜，藏在市中心小巷內，氣氛比街邊小店舒服，但菜式仍然保留越南家庭菜與街頭味道。放在最後一日午餐很適合：不用太 formal，但又可以把 bánh xèo、椰子炒飯、越式小食一次過收尾。</p></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Highlights</h2><ul><li>Bánh Xèo 黃金煎餅</li><li>椰子炒飯</li><li>越式拼盤與家常菜</li></ul></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Good to Know</h2><ul><li>入口在巷內，第一次去要跟 Google Maps 慢慢找。</li><li>多人 share 最好食，4 人比 2 人更適合。</li></ul></section></main><div class="mini-menu" id="guideMenu"><button onclick="openGuideCategory('ATTRACTIONS')"><span><span class="menu-title">📍 ATTRACTIONS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('CAFÉS')"><span><span class="menu-title">☕ CAFÉS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('EXPERIENCE')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍳 EXPERIENCE</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('RESTAURANTS')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍽 RESTAURANTS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SHOP')"><span><span class="menu-title">🛍 SHOP</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SPA')"><span><span class="menu-title">💆 SPA</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('STAY')"><span><span class="menu-title">🏨 STAY</span></span><span>›</span></button></div><div class="mini-menu" id="tripMenu">
