"_blank">🗺 Open Google Maps</a><button class="moment-button" onclick="openMomentsModal('book-street')">✨ Moment</button></div></section><section class="prose-block guide-overview"><h2>Overview</h2><p>Nguyễn Văn Bình Book Street 夾在郵政局與紅教堂旁邊，是短短一條步行文化街。書店、咖啡、文創攤位集中，適合在 Day 1 三大景點中作一個較輕鬆的過渡位。</p></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Highlights</h2><ul><li>步行書街</li><li>書店、文創、咖啡小攤</li><li>與郵政局／紅教堂相連</li></ul></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Good to Know</h2><ul><li>不是大型景點，停留 20–40 分鐘即可。</li><li>若太熱，可以只穿過拍照，不必硬逛每間店。</li></ul></section></main><div class="mini-menu" id="guideMenu"><button onclick="openGuideCategory('ATTRACTIONS')"><span><span class="menu-title">📍 ATTRACTIONS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('CAFÉS')"><span><span class="menu-title">☕ CAFÉS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('EXPERIENCE')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍳 EXPERIENCE</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('RESTAURANTS')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍽 RESTAURANTS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SHOP')"><span><span class="menu-title">🛍 SHOP</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SPA')"><span><span class="menu-title">💆 SPA</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('STAY')"><span><span class="menu-title">🏨 STAY</span></span><span>›</span></button></div><div class="mini-menu" id="tripMenu">
