button class="moment-button" onclick="openMomentsModal('cafe-apartments')">✨ Moment</button></div></section><section class="prose-block guide-overview"><h2>Overview</h2><p>The Cafe Apartments 係阮惠步行街最有代表性的老公寓改造景點。白天入內是迷宮式小店與 cafe，夜晚外牆一格格招牌亮起，反而成為最經典的西貢夜景背景。今次 Day 1 將 Spa 同夜景安排在同一棟樓，動線很聰明：下午上樓放鬆，晚上食完飯回來影霓虹燈。</p></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Highlights</h2><ul><li>夜晚外牆最上鏡</li><li>每層都有不同 cafe、選物店、香氛小店</li><li>電梯可能收小額費用，亦可逐層行樓梯探索</li></ul></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Good to Know</h2><ul><li>建議先搭到高層，再慢慢向下行，體力消耗較少。</li><li>不建議一入門就坐第一間；先逛一圈再決定。</li></ul></section></main><div class="mini-menu" id="guideMenu"><button onclick="openGuideCategory('ATTRACTIONS')"><span><span class="menu-title">📍 ATTRACTIONS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('CAFÉS')"><span><span class="menu-title">☕ CAFÉS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('EXPERIENCE')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍳 EXPERIENCE</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('RESTAURANTS')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍽 RESTAURANTS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SHOP')"><span><span class="menu-title">🛍 SHOP</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SPA')"><span><span class="menu-title">💆 SPA</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('STAY')"><span><span class="menu-title">🏨 STAY</span></span><span>›</span></button></div><div class="mini-menu" id="tripMenu">
