al('com-tam-moc')">✨ Moment</button></div></section><section class="prose-block guide-overview"><h2>Overview</h2><p>Cơm Tấm Mộc 是碎米飯的舒服版：保留炭烤豬排香氣，但環境比街邊小店乾淨、有冷氣。Day 2 早上放在 Cooking Class 前，重點是試一口地道早餐，而不是食到太飽。</p></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Highlights</h2><ul><li>炭烤豬排碎米飯</li><li>魚露、蛋、酸菜配搭</li><li>冷氣環境比街邊舒服</li></ul></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Good to Know</h2><ul><li>4 人點 2–3 份 share 已足夠，因為 10:00 還有 cooking class。</li><li>如果早上不餓，可以改成外帶咖啡。</li></ul></section></main><div class="mini-menu" id="guideMenu"><button onclick="openGuideCategory('ATTRACTIONS')"><span><span class="menu-title">📍 ATTRACTIONS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('CAFÉS')"><span><span class="menu-title">☕ CAFÉS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('EXPERIENCE')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍳 EXPERIENCE</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('RESTAURANTS')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍽 RESTAURANTS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SHOP')"><span><span class="menu-title">🛍 SHOP</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SPA')"><span><span class="menu-title">💆 SPA</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('STAY')"><span><span class="menu-title">🏨 STAY</span></span><span>›</span></button></div><div class="mini-menu" id="tripMenu">
