yn')">✨ Moment</button></div></section><section class="prose-block guide-overview"><h2>Overview</h2><p>NOSBYN 是越南本地較成熟的極簡女裝品牌，重點不是花巧，而是布料、剪裁和耐穿度。它適合買襯衫、連身裙、外套等 timeless 單品，風格像 COS 的簡潔版，但線條更女性化。</p></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Highlights</h2><ul><li>Minimal / timeless 女裝</li><li>布料質感與剪裁較穩</li><li>Office、旅行、日常都可重複穿</li></ul></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Good to Know</h2><ul><li>顏色偏 neutral，啱鍾意低調質感的人。</li><li>熱門尺碼可能不齊，看到喜歡要即試。</li></ul></section></main><div class="mini-menu" id="guideMenu"><button onclick="openGuideCategory('ATTRACTIONS')"><span><span class="menu-title">📍 ATTRACTIONS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('CAFÉS')"><span><span class="menu-title">☕ CAFÉS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('EXPERIENCE')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍳 EXPERIENCE</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('RESTAURANTS')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍽 RESTAURANTS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SHOP')"><span><span class="menu-title">🛍 SHOP</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SPA')"><span><span class="menu-title">💆 SPA</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('STAY')"><span><span class="menu-title">🏨 STAY</span></span><span>›</span></button></div><div class="mini-menu" id="tripMenu">
