')">✨ Moment</button></div></section><section class="prose-block guide-overview"><h2>Overview</h2><p>OHQUAO 是比較有藝術感的 Thảo Điền 小店，適合找明信片、香氛、手工小物和不太 mass-market 的 souvenir。比起商場手信，這裡更像旅行中途發現的小寶物。</p></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Highlights</h2><ul><li>在地藝術家小物</li><li>明信片、香氛、家居手信</li><li>適合買輕便 souvenir</li></ul></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Good to Know</h2><ul><li>不要預期大型店鋪，這類小店重點是慢慢看。</li><li>適合安排在 Mộc Hương Spa 前後順路逛。</li></ul></section></main><div class="mini-menu" id="guideMenu"><button onclick="openGuideCategory('ATTRACTIONS')"><span><span class="menu-title">📍 ATTRACTIONS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('CAFÉS')"><span><span class="menu-title">☕ CAFÉS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('EXPERIENCE')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍳 EXPERIENCE</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('RESTAURANTS')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍽 RESTAURANTS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SHOP')"><span><span class="menu-title">🛍 SHOP</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SPA')"><span><span class="menu-title">💆 SPA</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('STAY')"><span><span class="menu-title">🏨 STAY</span></span><span>›</span></button></div><div class="mini-menu" id="tripMenu">
