✨ Moment</button></div></section><section class="prose-block guide-overview"><h2>Overview</h2><p>Quince Saigon 是最後一晚很適合的 farewell dinner。它以 wood-fired cooking、charcoal grill 和開放式廚房聞名，菜式有火烤香氣但不會太難懂。氣氛成熟、燈光暗、服務穩定，適合四人旅行最後一晚坐低慢慢回味。</p></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Highlights</h2><ul><li>Wood-fired / charcoal-grilled dishes</li><li>Open kitchen / counter seats</li><li>成熟但不拘謹的 farewell dinner 氣氛</li></ul></section><section class="prose-block"><h2>Good to Know</h2><ul><li>如果想看廚房動作，可嘗試要求 counter seats。</li><li>燈光偏暗，影相未必最清楚，但氣氛很好。</li></ul></section></main><div class="mini-menu" id="guideMenu"><button onclick="openGuideCategory('ATTRACTIONS')"><span><span class="menu-title">📍 ATTRACTIONS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('CAFÉS')"><span><span class="menu-title">☕ CAFÉS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('EXPERIENCE')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍳 EXPERIENCE</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('RESTAURANTS')"><span><span class="menu-title">🍽 RESTAURANTS</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SHOP')"><span><span class="menu-title">🛍 SHOP</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('SPA')"><span><span class="menu-title">💆 SPA</span></span><span>›</span></button><button onclick="openGuideCategory('STAY')"><span><span class="menu-title">🏨 STAY</span></span><span>›</span></button></div><div class="mini-menu" id="tripMenu">
